OL,7,FSpeaking at St George's Hospital in
OL,8,FTooting, south-west London, she said:
OL,9,F"Getting an official certificate means
OL,10,Fa lot.
OL,12,F"Parents feel it's so important to see
OL,13,Ftheir baby's name on a certificate
OL,14,Fthat they can share with family, and
OL,15,Ffriends and remember that baby.
OL,17,F"We've had parents user-testing the
OL,18,Fsystem which is why it's taken a
OL,19,Flittle bit longer to get up and
OL,20,Frunning than we would have liked.
OL,26,@qD@AOUtD@AOUyD@AOU
