OL,7,F"It's a very difficult time for
OL,8,Fparents, even if they don't do it
OL,9,Fstraight away... so we want to make it
OL,10,Fas easy as possible."
OL,12,FThe minister was shown around the
OL,13,Funit's specialist bereavement suite,
OL,14,Fwhich offers a comforting and private
OL,15,Fsetting for families dealing with the
OL,16,Femotional and physical challenges of
OL,17,Fperinatal loss.
