OL,12,FThe minister said: "Having a facility
OL,13,Flike this where mums are not on a
OL,14,Fmaternity ward, where they have the
OL,15,Ftime and space to spend with their
OL,16,Fbaby before they have to leave
OL,17,Fhospital is crucial.
