OL,7,FAsked about calls to introduce
OL,8,Fstatutory leave for bereaved parents
OL,9,Fwho have lost a baby before 24 weeks,
OL,10,Fshe said: "We are looking at that. As
OL,11,Fa department, we're leading the way in
OL,12,Fsupporting employees at the Department
OL,13,Fof Health and Social Care.
OL,15,F"There's nothing formal at the moment,
OL,16,Fbut a bit like we've done with the
OL,17,Fmenopause, in encouraging employers to
OL,18,Flook after their staff, both mums and
OL,19,Fdads. It's really important.
OL,26,@rD@KOUwD@AOU
