OL,7,FKath Abrahams, chief executive of
OL,8,FTommy's, the pregnancy research and
OL,9,Fbaby loss charity, told ITV News:
OL,10,F"We're really pleased that the
OL,11,Fgovernment has introduced baby loss
OL,12,Fcertificates, but we'd also like to
OL,13,Fsee a strong commitment from
OL,14,Fgovernment to collecting and recording
OL,15,Fthe number of miscarriages that happen
OL,16,Fevery year.
OL,18,F"Unless we record the data,
OL,19,Fmiscarriage largely remains a hidden
OL,20,Fproblem," she added.
